  "Factory Rework HFM or CID PAIRING - Scenario error": {
   "width": 10140,
   "height": 9780,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY REWORK : HFM or Customer ID pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 15,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1560,
      "height": 1245,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Complete the \"After Sales code\" ( 16 bytes) and press the button \"ENTER REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 690,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for HFM pairing is launched, then insert a customer ID belonging to the vehicle in the reader or switch Ignition Power Supply ON",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 1065,
      "width": 4800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Once all the customer IDs are paired, select \"Validate\", and press the button \"EXIT REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5160,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 4560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / HFM information",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5160,
      "top": 6000,
      "height": 3750,
      "width": 4545
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " CID ANALYSE",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 360,
      "height": 1125,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7920,
      "height": 1845,
      "width": 4800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Rework Mode failure ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6000,
      "height": 1815,
      "width": 4800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Pairing\" to pair a customer ID",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5160,
      "top": 3840,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 4560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for customer ID pairing is launched, then insert a customer ID (belonging to the vehicle or blank) in the reader or switch Ignition Power Supply ON",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5160,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 990,
      "width": 4560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
