  "CID AFTER SALES PAIRING": {
   "width": 12420,
   "height": 10980,
   "color": "rgb(0,64,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : Customer ID pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(39,198,216)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Approach the customer ID to the Kazashi ring and press \"CID Analyse\" to check its status",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 2760,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Complete the PARAMETER_CID_PAIRING (8 bytes - optional) Then press \"Request Server CID pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3120,
      "height": 1680,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Copy the Input_Data_To_Server into the Code Server, get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes), and paste it into \"SERVER ANSWER\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 4200,
      "height": 1080,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Complete the \"Additional pairing datas\" (11 bytes - optional) then press \"Transmit Server Answer\"  ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 5280,
      "height": 1320,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) If the HFM is SA unlocked for CID pairing, approach a blank CID to the ring and press \"CID pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 6600,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) Repeat Step 5/ for all CID to pair",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 7320,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID ANALYSE",
     "color": "rgb(118,113,227)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 1440,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 8280,
      "height": 2400,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Return Code",
     "color": "rgb(192,192,192)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 1320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Courier New",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "1"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Return Code",
     "color": "rgb(192,192,192)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 6960,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 1320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Courier New",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "1"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Debug Information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6480,
      "top": 8280,
      "height": 2400,
      "width": 5760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "REQ: Connect to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" : https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login and enter your IPN and Password",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 2400,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "1"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) Exit Pairing Procedure",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 7800,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
